\`\`\`
Recent Altitude Gain + Symptoms
       |
       v
Is headache present?
  No → Consider alternative diagnosis
  Yes → + One other symptom?
          |
          +--- No → Monitor, symptomatic care
          |
          +--- Yes → AMS present
                  |
                  v
              Lake Louise Score?
                  |
                  +--- <4 → Rest, hydrate, analgesics
                  +--- 4-6 → Stop ascent, consider descent
