                  |
                  v
              Ataxia or confusion?
                  |
                  +--- Yes → HACE: Descent + O2 + Dexamethasone
                  +--- No → Dyspnea at rest?
                            |
                            +--- Yes → HAPE: Descent + O2 + Nifedipine
                            +--- No → Continue AMS protocol
\`\`\`

## Research Frontiers

- Genetic testing for susceptibility (EPAS1, EGLN1, eNOS)
- Point-of-care biomarkers (copeptin, sST2, NGAL)
- Novel pulmonary vasodilators
- Hypoxic preconditioning protocols
- Personalized ascent profiles
